    <briefdescription>
<para>Frame metadata header carried in every ZMQ message. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The first 4 bytes of the wire header are always the magic value <computeroutput>0x53494753</computeroutput> (&quot;SIGS&quot;), which receivers can use for basic validation. Future-proofed for DIFI / VITA 49 with protocol and stream_id fields. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
